469
00:42:53,149 --> 00:42:56,550
-Touching, isn't it?
-Get used to it, Branner.

470
00:42:56,853 --> 00:42:59,014
lt'll follow us all the way.

471
00:43:00,056 --> 00:43:02,820
Good to be back with you
after all these years, Doc.

472
00:43:02,892 --> 00:43:04,325
Look at him.

473
00:43:04,393 --> 00:43:07,055
Ten pounds of trousers
for two pounds of rump.

474
00:43:09,832 --> 00:43:12,995
You weren't so funny
back in Cape Town, were you?

475
00:43:13,102 --> 00:43:17,163
When you came crying to me
with a very far gone venereal disease...

476
00:43:17,240 --> 00:43:19,731
which l found almost impossible to cure.

477
